java.lang.Object
  de.thesycon.usbio.structs.USBIO_DATA_BUFFER
public class USBIO_DATA_BUFFER
extends java.lang.Object

The USBIO_DATA_BUFFER class is used for buffer input/output operations with the UsbIo Java Interface.
